properties.title: Swakopmund Aquarium
properties.description: The National Marine Aquarium of Namibia is located in the coastal town of Swakopmund, wedged between the mighty Atlantic Ocean and the Namib Desert.

properties.title: The Kristall Galerie
properties.description: The Kristall Galerie located in Swakopmund, Namibia was founded in 1998 showcasing a variety of specimens, crystals and cut gemstones.
